---
title: Jalapeño Popper Burgers with Sweet Potato Fries and Garlic Mayo
description: It’s fall sports season and we’ve got tailgate food on the brain—it doesn’t get much better than sharing some grub with all of your fellow fans, right? Our chefs translated those game-day flavors into something you can whip up any night of the week with these jalapeño popper burgers. They have cheese stuffed inside a juicy patty and are topped with garlic mayo and slices of the spicy chili pepper. Plus, with sweet potato wedges on the side, they’re definitely going to score a dinnertime touchdown.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/jalapeno-popper-burgers-03f9f478.jpg
